title: Rug Doctor Portable Spot Cleaner Solutions
description: We've developed four different solutions to use with your Portable Spot Cleaner. Learn what each solution helps eliminate!

asset.author: Rug Doctor LLC
asset.description: We've developed four different solutions to use with your Portable Spot Cleaner. Learn what each solution helps eliminate!

transcripts: To help keep every soft surface in your life fresh and clean we've developed four different solutions to use with your portable spot cleaner. The pet solution is formulated to permanently remove oil-based pet stains and odors from soft surfaces and carpets. The area rug solution is perfect for, you guessed it permanently removing spots and stains from area rugs without harming the delicate fibers. Sofa and chair solution is designed specifically for thoroughly washing spots stains and odors out of upholstery. And if you have vehicle related stains like motor oil lubricant or tar use the vehicle solution to permanently remove them from your cars upholstered interior. All four rug doctor solutions are designed for any rug doctor cleaning machine and can also be used as a spot treatment. A portable deep down clean anytime, anywhere. Let's get cleaning.
